      <h2 xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"> <span class="mw-headline" id="Production">Production</span></h2>
      <p xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">According to Curtis, <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_Mitchum" title="Robert Mitchum">Robert Mitchum</a> was the first choice to play Jackson but did not want to work with a black actor. Kramer wrote that Poitier was initially unsure of Curtis' casting but became supportive. Curtis, however, denied this; he stated that he had contractual rights to approve who would play Cullen, and that he requested <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Billing_(filmmaking)#Main_billing" title="Billing (filmmaking)">Poitier's name appear with his</a> in the <a class="external" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Opening_credits" title="Opening credits">opening credits</a>.</p>
